{"tid":1283060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【撐警撐政府係唯一出路】","createTime":"2019-07-03T17:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T17:49:24.000Z","uid":72555,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd57b05230cc2f94864428870960b64fdac1f0c8","tid":1283060,"uid":72555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"和理非非派做嘅嘢係咪一直唔夠膠？太認真，對呢個世界好多人真係冇影響，哪怕去到和理非非嘅公民抗命，突顯唔到制度不公，但又付上代價。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱諗到，唔知work唔work，即管Up下睇吓咩反應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>做個正義報警L，見到違泊就報。</strong><br />\n1）完全合法，高舉官員所講嘅「法治」<br />\n2）讓活喺平衡時空嘅人（可應係車主啦）知道香港不平安<br />\n3）冇得話攪亂香港啊，依家你犯法，警察執法<br />\n4）立會需要錢維修，愛港人士一於幫手搵眾籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果真係做，身邊又有人有車，可以單聲叫佢做個奉公守法好市民獎個孝仔幫佢食一張，叫佢下次唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ea805b063740f0a9904b8bb86a946c7fbb8c42","tid":1283060,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"發夢見到夜晚好多車拍街<br />\n唔知投訴有無用呢夜晚"},{"pid":"b0b3a94ee2c0846e43fb7728a94c4e51ea1e7133","tid":1283060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ea805b063740f0a9904b8bb86a946c7fbb8c42","tid":1283060,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:10:15.000Z","msg":"發夢見到夜晚好多車拍街<br />\n唔知投訴有無用呢夜晚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"1823"},{"pid":"bd6d3019b16f7685f91b328585fa71978e5aff74","tid":1283060,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我無嘢講&nbsp;<br />\n我有權唔解鎖電話&nbsp;<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我唔會簽任何文件<br />\n我要食飯 要毛氈 去廁所</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cadab26291eb543aab4541a6f902299e550a046f","tid":1283060,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b3a94ee2c0846e43fb7728a94c4e51ea1e7133","tid":1283060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ea805b063740f0a9904b8bb86a946c7fbb8c42","tid":